# Library Management System

A microservices-based library management system built with
Java 17, Spring Boot 3.2, Spring Cloud, Hibernate, and MySQL.

## Services

| Service | Port | Description |
|---------|------|-------------|
| eureka-server | 8761 | Service registry |
| api-gateway | 8080 | Entry point, JWT filter, routing |
| user-service | 8081 | Registration, login, JWT auth |
| book-service | 8082 | Book catalog and inventory |
| borrow-service | 8083 | Checkout and return |
| notification-service | 8084 | Email notifications via Kafka |

## Quick Start
```bash
# 1. Start infrastructure (MySQL + Kafka)
docker-compose up -d mysql kafka zookeeper

# 2. Start services in order
cd eureka-server      && mvn spring-boot:run &
cd api-gateway        && mvn spring-boot:run &
cd user-service       && mvn spring-boot:run &
cd book-service       && mvn spring-boot:run &
cd borrow-service     && mvn spring-boot:run &
cd notification-service && mvn spring-boot:run &
```

## Tech Stack
- Java 17 · Spring Boot 3.2 · Spring Cloud 2023
- Spring Security · JJWT · Spring Data JPA · Hibernate
- MySQL 8 · Apache Kafka
- Docker · GitHub Actions
